  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A randomized controlled pilot study to compare the efficacy and tolerability of a two&#xD;
      different NIV masks on carbon dioxide in participants with stable chronic obstructive&#xD;
      pulmonary disease (COPD) with chronic type II respiratory failure.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
